reviewtext: I bought a pair of these for home because I kept loosing my earbuds.These sound better than the $200 beats HD headphones my son bought.Of the headphones I've used here's where I would rate them(Worst on top)Imitation apple earbuds ($3) (sound quality 1 out of 10)Apple earbuds ($30)  (sound quality 3-4 out of 10)Senheiser in ear adidas sport earbuds ($60) (Sound quality 3-4 out of 10)Beats HD Solo ($200 ripoff) (sound quality 5 out of 10)Panasonic HT21 ($4) (sound quality 6 out of 10)Senheiser HD280 Pro ($100) (sound quality 9 out of 10)(Best on bottom)These are really an amazing set of headphones.They would easily be a good value if the price was $20. At $3-5 they are a steal.
summary: Simply awesome at 10-20 times the cost
